Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.61,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:42.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us how to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:51.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't let us feed it like this if it easily bit people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:01:59.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:02.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing sure is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if dinosaurs were like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.90,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. There you go talking like a\Nchild again while trying to act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:13.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:19.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this place is so empty that it's almost uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, could it be that we have this place all to ourselves today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they keep operating like this, considering\Nthe cost of the feed and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:34.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually from a warm country, but\Nit's been brought to such a cold place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:39.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good number of giraffes in Japan, but\Nit's not like it'll ever meet another of its kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:43.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and will spend the rest of its life here in\Nsolitude without ever speaking to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:46.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:53.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Mister Giraffe have to be brought to a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably so kids in countries where giraffes\Ncan't normally be seen can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:59.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why isn't anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look! You're a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:22.18,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing her face and her unblinking eyes, I realize that\Nshe was sketching with her eyes, ears, nose, and brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:29.11,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,After memorizing this whole scene with the giraffe, she'll\Nprobably spit it all out onto a canvas back in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.11,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,...whether she absorbs all of it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:35.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.04,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's done memorizing it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try giving it a carrot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:44.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get an upset stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second, I'll go buy another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. It's just that your kick seems\Nto have gotten even sharper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:27.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure you aren't so quick to hit your superiors\Nand coworkers once you're working for a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also been turned down by every company I've applied to so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still waiting for my results myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.81,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.98,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,So he ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've wanted to tell me something since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:12.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone from another office who I worked with told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:18.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that there was someone who lived with\NRika-san for a while after her accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, wasn't it, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way, it sounds risqué, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:28.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was probably just on the lookout...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make sure that Rika didn't follow him in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:41.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a kid from the country who liked to\Ndraw, even though I wasn't that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no confidence, but lots of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:48.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I didn't fit in anywhere and\Njust concentrated on drawing on canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.71,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada was a mysterious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:07.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when he was laughing casually, being with him\Nmade you feel like he could see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't feel uncomfortable with that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:15.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we worked part time together and moved\Nto a run-down apartment, though it had a yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:15.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord1\be1\shad0\move(640,81,496,81)\c&HD9DDDE&\3c&H7E7573&}Yamashita Realtors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:15.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\be1\shad0\i1\frz23\fs21\move(333,160,188,160)\3c&H3A5071&\c&H77ADC6&}Apartments
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magpie and a white-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuuji, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.66,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Phone — 000-0000 {\be1\3c&H000000&}Harada\NWe're taking care of a lost dog!! (Akita breed)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And towards the end of our third year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:26.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally tamed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Egami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika was a girl from Hokkaido who was terribly good at drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:46.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was known around campus as the "Snow Queen"\Ndue to her beauty and unfriendliness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was the center of attention of the guys there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she's been half disowned by her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be really tired from her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so thin that it's only skin and bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing. We're having nabe tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.78,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Nabe: {\be1\3c&H000000&}traditional Japanese meal with a variety\Nof ingredients cooked together in a hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have us three eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:10.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:11.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu's cooking is the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada, let her eat at her leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:24.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, Harada might've picked up both Rika and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like those cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:31.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, the three of us lived together in that apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:36.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...until Harada and Rika decided to get married, became independent, and moved into that office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:42.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was the same, as if it was a matter\Nof fact, and things were ridiculously fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:45.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Rika's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama... kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:08.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for coming in without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a terrible accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:18.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If a passing truck driver hadn't pulled\NRika out, she would've burned up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:24.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the night after the opening party for the store\Nthey had designed, and they were both really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika was the one driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had stayed at the party without going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had left before it started snowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had left their car there and taken a taxi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they hadn't taken that road...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:46.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As if she was being cornered by the possibilities\Nthat could no longer be realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rika started pushing her disabled body to\Nwork on the jobs that Harada left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave Rika's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:09:00.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I commuted to work from that office and\Ncame back to help her work at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:03.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried that I would lose even Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stand the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you leave her side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika began trying to distance herself from even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:19.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada's existence was too significant for both her and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:23.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When Rika and I were together, we couldn't help but\Nreminisce about when all three of us were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:29.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I began to think that it might have\Nbeen better to let her follow Harada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I started thinking that, I couldn't be around her any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:39.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I need to get away, cool\Nmy mind, and stabilize the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you recommended me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all the guys I knew, you seemed to be the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:56.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...who could handle things the best without delving\Ntoo much into other people's problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a terrible way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I never would've expected it to turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:11.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan! Let's ride on the ferris wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:16.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Rika has already asked me\Nto introduce a new part-timer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My actual acceptance letter hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika said that you'd definitely be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:27.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About Rika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Harada and Rika were different from something\Nas simple as friends or lovers to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They were simply important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:43.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived in the same room, ate the same\Nfood, and breathed the same air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:47.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to think of them as a part of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to say something out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Mayama good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:05.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I end up taking advantage of him because I know that he likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just avail yourself to him and take advantage of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:14.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I push away and hurt him but still keep him by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:18.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an acceptable way for people to interact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I was being bolstered by his wounded heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:28.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was happy to hear that he decided to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Four more days until the due date...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.20,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(513,307)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:56.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(466,321)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:56.41,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(422,334)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:56.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(377,346)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:56.70,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(333,360)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:56.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(332,372)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A3B39&\fs38\shad0\bord0\pos(331,384)}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm gonna finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:04.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to start early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:06.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Hagu-chan, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaa! Yamada, how can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My steamed buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I've already submitted my graduate thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\frz48\pos(477,44)\bord1\shad0\be1\c&H676CB5&}gaaaan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:22.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I heard that you made\Nan amazing piece, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An amazing piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:54.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada! Yamada! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the legendary large bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouda-sensei said that it excited him so\Nmuch that his blood pressure went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it was just somewhat big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you couldn't get a job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:19.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Morita writes the name of his murder\Nwith tea on the floor (Yamada).
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The going is t-t-ough for g-g-g-girls right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But y-you're sticking around as a g-g-g-g-graduate\Nstudent, r-right, Y-Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:25.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad actually told me to carry on the family\Nsake business with my older brother, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:30.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought that as a woman, I wouldn't\Nbe able to handle being a sake maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:38.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try again in two years after I obtain more\Nqualifications as a graduate student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about qualifications, you can always talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:44.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, the rest of you should get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have four more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:55.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you pass your employment exam,\Nit would be silly if you couldn't graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:56.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:00.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come. There's no time for you to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and finish your graduate thesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:16.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me retire already. At this rate, my life will end first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.11,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs17\an4\move(365,172,365,115)\c&H84634F&}Sender: Tokudaiji\NDate:     20XX/01/XX\NHanamoto Research Lab\NRegarding the Field Work
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.11,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs20\an4\move(390,280,390,222)\c&H84634F&}Hanamoto-kun,\N\NI'm awaiting your response regarding the\Nfield work. I'm coming to Tokyo this week,\Nso I'd like to speak to you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some fried rolls and croquette\Nbread at the Maruei Bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to carry this around with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:15.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just why do you think I synchronized\Nit with my car's navigation system?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:18.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:30.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. Want some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:50.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Please give me coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! It's been a while, Takaido-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:11.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'll do my best! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Design Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Design Office? You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:24.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did they call you directly instead\Nof our employment department?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:30.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I sometimes helped them out when\Nwe worked at the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... But I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:38.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you've already been semi-tested\Nduring the past year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama... So you got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, fortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Tange-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here! That idiot isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the graduate thesis is due in 30 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was 90% finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:03.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He left the last 10% and disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:06.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I haven't seen\Nhim in the last two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a statue of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is it macho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares anymore, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:20.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can entitle it "Useless."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.90,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\be1\3c&H000000&}The word "{\be0\3c&H635514&}hanninmae{\be1\3c&H000000&}" ("useless") literally means "half a man."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But while I'm still alive, I can't accept\Nsomething that's incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world did this to Gramps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:47.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, congratulations on submitting your\Ngraduate thesis and emergency thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:54.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, the only one out of this\Ngroup who will go away is Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a guy like him, it's a little sad to see him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:02.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, he won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:14.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he hates being left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:18.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, it ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:28.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Mayama... About the new part-timer\NRika asked me to look for...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:34.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Should it be a guy or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:36.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.48,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It involves physical labor, so a guy would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.35,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but putting an unfamiliar brat in that room with Rika-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.48,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but on the other hand, she'll have\Nto be more courteous around a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.32,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a guy, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.40,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of a company called Art Craft?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Asai-san's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. I've worked with them a few times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:04.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be working with them on a cooperative project for a\Nwhile and apparently doesn't need a part-timer for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.88,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! There's nothing to worry about if that Asai-san is with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.54,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGreetings\1a&H16&\fs45\bord3\be1\shad0\pos(450,46)\fad(250,250)\3c&HFDF9F6&\c&H70594F&}Asai-san      A gentleman in his fifties
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:14.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, wake up, everyone. Let's go home and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:19.68,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika, I sort of understand why you\Nweren't able to let go of Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:26.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Mayama, I'm leaving now,\Nso please lock the door behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Yamada, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You take her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:35.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure that she doesn't need\Nto get drunk like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:47.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab on tight. You'll fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, that's too tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:59.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yamada... Why did you fall in love wih me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:09.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been thinking that I needed to turn you down\Nproperly if you ever told me that you liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:15.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I thought that you'd go away somewhere if I turned you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:21.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked at you, it hurt me because\Nit was like looking at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "Ah, I wonder if I look like\Nthat from Rika-san's perspective..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncool and persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:33.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I tried to act cool, I couldn't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:45.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wasn't able to give up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, are you drooling on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:53.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:04.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:10.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:12.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:14.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
